Appendix 1:

ANSWERS TO POST-HEARING QUESTIONS

(127)

VerDate 11-MAY-2000 17:40 Sep 17, 2005 Jkt 020007 PO 00000 Frm 00131 Fmt 6601 Sfmt 6601 C:\WORKD\SA05\031605\20007 SCIENCE1 PsN: SCIENCE1

